**********************
* Ignited Datatables *
**********************

Ignited Datatables is a wrapper class/library for Datatables (table plug-in for Jquery) 

Standalone Php Library:
Fork   : https://github.com/n1crack/IgnitedDatatables-php-library
Discuss: http://datatables.net/forums/discussion/5133/ignited-datatables-php-library

Codeigniter Library:
Fork   : https://github.com/IgnitedDatatables/Ignited-Datatables
Discuss: http://ellislab.com/forums/viewthread/160896/

Contact: Vincent Bambico <metal.conspiracy@gmail.com>
         Yusuf Ozdemir <yusuf@ozdemir.be>

Features:
1. Easy to use. Generates json using only a few lines of code.
2. Support for table joins (left, right, outer, inner, left outer, right outer).
3. Able to define custom columns, and filters.
4. Editable custom variables with callback function support.
5. Supports generation of tables using non utf-8 charsets.
6. mDataprop support!
7. Auto detects HTTP method (POST or GET) //only native php version

You can download the db (sakila) for examples from: http://dev.mysql.com/doc/index-other.html

============
Requirements
============
jQuery 1.5+
DataTables 1.7+ (Pref 1.8.1+)

